OL,3,CWelsh family 'stranded' in Dubai after
OL,4,Cair strikes cause travel chaos
OL,6,FA family from Bridgend are stuck in
OL,7,FDubai following a wave of air strikes
OL,8,Fin the region.
OL,10,FGulf nations have become targets for
OL,11,FIran as it lashes out against
OL,12,FAmerica's allies in retaliation for
OL,13,Fthe strikes on its territory over the
OL,14,Fweekend.
OL,16,FThis has led to the airspace in some
OL,17,Fof the world's most important travel
OL,18,Fhubs being closed for the foreseeable
OL,19,Ffuture.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
