OL,3,CWelsh family 'stranded' in Dubai after
OL,4,Cair strikes cause travel chaos
OL,6,FAbout half a million passengers use
OL,7,Fairports in Dubai, Doha or Abu Dhabi
OL,8,Feach day.
OL,10,FLiam Skyrme and his partner and
OL,11,Fchildren were due to fly home from
OL,12,FDubai on Monday 2nd March, but their
OL,13,Fflight was cancelled just two hours
OL,14,Fbefore take-off.
OL,16,F"Saturday everything just turned
OL,17,Fupside down," Mr Skyrme said. "The
OL,18,Flast two days, we've heard bombs or
OL,19,Fbombs being intercepted.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772539378
OL,3,CWelsh family 'stranded' in Dubai after
OL,4,Cair strikes cause travel chaos
OL,6,F"Our phone alarms went off when there
OL,7,Fwas an upcoming air strike. We all
OL,8,Fevacuated to the basement for two
OL,9,Fdays," Mr Skyrme said. "It's been
OL,10,Fquite overwhelming, to be fair.
OL,12,F"In my head, I thought I was going
OL,13,Fhome today. It's been upsetting and
OL,14,Fwith the children, it's been
OL,15,Ftraumatising."
OL,17,FThe British government believes
OL,18,Fhundreds of thousands of UK citizens
OL,19,Fare in the region, and is now drawing
OL,20,Fup plans to evacuate them.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772539378
OL,3,CWelsh family 'stranded' in Dubai after
OL,4,Cair strikes cause travel chaos
OL,6,FMr Skyrme says he has not been able to
OL,7,Freach Emirates for assistance. "They
OL,8,Fhave a dedicated phone line, but the
OL,9,Fline is engaged. I have not actually
OL,10,Fspoken with any airlines," he said.
OL,12,F"My plan is to book an additional
OL,13,Fflight as soon as we know, but right
OL,14,Fnow nobody knows."
OL,16,FWhile some amenities at their resort
OL,17,Fhave begun to reopen, Mr Skyrme says
OL,18,Fthey have not ventured out since
OL,19,FSaturday 28th February.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
